description.displayText: Veronica is an incredibly kind, smart, and amazing teacher. She is knowledgeable in multiple subject areas and is incredibly patient when working with students of all abilities. She is organized and prepares detailed and thoughtful lesson plans. She cares deeply about the students she works with, and works hard to help them to succeed. Veronica is thoughtful and tailors lessons and teaching strategies to the individual needs of the student she is working with. She is a wonderful teacher and person to work with!
